des: I'm Olabot. I’m here to help you create a virtual version of you! Along the way you'll have a lot of fun and also learn about your friends! You'll teach me all kinds of stuff about yourself, what you like, dislike and how you think. Then your friends can talk to me to learn about you and see what surprising things you have in common.
